# CLIP ChangeLog for net-misc/openssh

*openssh-7.5_p1-r5 (12 Feb 2018)

  12 Feb 2018; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openssh-7.5_p1-r5.ebuild, -openssh-7.5_p1-r4.ebuild:
  RBump for linux-headers 4.4 rebuild.

*openssh-7.5_p1-r4 (28 Nov 2017)

  28 Nov 2017; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openssh-7.5_p1-r4.ebuild, -openssh-7.5_p1-r3.ebuild:
  Force rebuild with RGS compliant crypto parameter

*openssh-7.5_p1-r3 (20 Nov 2017)

  20 Nov 2017; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openssh-7.5_p1-r3.ebuild, -openssh-7.5_p1-r2.ebuild:
  Refresh configuration to remove deprecated options and improve crypto
  parameters

*openssh-7.5_p1-r2 (18 Sep 2017)

  18 Sep 2017; Nicolas Godinho <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openssh-7.5_p1-r2.ebuild, -openssh-7.5_p1-r1.ebuild:
  Rbump to fix sshd init script which had /sbin/openrc-run as shebang. This
  binary superseding /sbin/runscript does not exist in CLIP due to OpenRC being
  too old.

*openssh-7.5_p1-r1 (07 Sep 2017)

  07 Sep 2017; Nicolas Godinho <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openssh-7.5_p1-r1.ebuild, -openssh-7.2_p2-r2.ebuild:
  Update to 7.5_p1-r1.

*openssh-7.2_p2-r2 (02 Sep 2016)

  02 Sep 2016; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openssh-7.2_p2-r2.ebuild, -openssh-7.2_p2-r1.ebuild:
  Rbump to add a clean delta between CLIP 4.4.2 and 4.4.3, needed for
  virtual/os-headers hard dependencies.

*openssh-7.2_p2-r1 (02 Sep 2016)

  02 Sep 2016; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +openssh-7.2_p2-r1.ebuild, -openssh-7.2_p2.ebuild:
  Rbump to fix the version delta between CLIP 4.4.2 and 4.4.3 - Re-enhance
  pre-auth process sandboxing.

